content.text:
## TASK
Generate a multi-provider image prompt pack for professional headshots and portraits.

## INPUTS
- Subject Description: {{subject_description}}
- Style: {{portrait_style}}
- Background: {{background}}
- Expression: {{expression}}
- Attire: {{attire}}

## CONSTRAINTS
- Output must be pure JSON (no markdown fences)
- Focus on professional, approachable appearance
- Avoid unrealistic or heavily stylized results
- Ensure proper lighting for flattering portraits

## OUTPUT FORMAT
Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "intent": "headshot",
  "providers": {
    "midjourney_v6": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "ar": "3:4", "stylize": 50 },
      "instructions": "..."
    },
    "sdxl": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "width": 768, "height": 1024, "steps": 35, "cfg": 7 }
    }
  },
  "notes": ["usage tips"]
}

## QUALITY CHECKS
- [ ] Subject clearly described
- [ ] Professional appearance maintained
- [ ] Lighting appropriate for portraits
- [ ] No markdown in output
